  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Thread the pita bread, nduja, pickle, and garlic onto skewers.",
    "Brush the skewers with olive oil and season with sumac.",
    "Grill the skewers for 5 minutes per side.",
    "Serve the skewers on a talavera plate with a side of lemon juice.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
